\q1
\v 2  \w For|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \nd Lord\nd* \w will|strong="H3581"\w* \w restore|strong="H5927"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* majesty \w of|strong="H6440"\w* Jacob,  
